### 8. Test 404 behavior for non-existing ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/model/driver/complex/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

> {%
    client.test("Request should return 404 NotFound", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 404, "Expected HTTP 404");
    });
%}